Package org.codice.ddf.migration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigurationMigratable
    Base interface that must be implemented by all bundles or features that need to export and/or import system related settings (e.g.
    DataMigratable
    Interface that must be implemented by all bundles or features that need to export and/or import data during system migration.
    Migratable
    This interface provides the mechanism for implementers to define how their data shall be exported for later import into a new system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DescribableBean
    This class may serve as a base for any service that provides the Describable methods from injectable data.
    MigrationMetadata
    This class provides metadata with details of a Migratable's export.
    MigrationWarning
    Class that provides statuses for migration operations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExportMigrationException
    Exception that indicates some problem when exporting the system' configurations.
    MigrationException
    Exception that indicates some problem with the configuration migration.
    UnexpectedMigrationException
    Exception that indicates an unexpected error during migration.
